{"id":4654,"date":"2021-05-10T10:23:45","date_gmt":"2021-05-10T08:23:45","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/154.0.202.153\/?post_type=dt_team&#038;p=4654"},"modified":"2025-04-12T12:43:26","modified_gmt":"2025-04-12T10:43:26","slug":"naruseb-alpheus","status":"publish","type":"dt_team","link":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/dt_team\/naruseb-alpheus\/","title":{"rendered":"!Naruseb, Alpheus"},"content":{"rendered":"<table width=\"100%\" align=\"left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-18829\" src=\"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/Alpheus-Naruseb-1-212x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"212\" height=\"300\" \/><\/td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"contact-position\"><strong>Member of Parliament &#8211; National Assembly <\/strong><\/p>\n<p class=\"contact-street\">Address: Private Bag 13323, Windhoek<\/p>\n<p class=\"contact-country\">SWAPO Party<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"25%\"><strong>Legislative Profile<\/strong><\/td>\n<td valign=\"top\">SWAPO party\u2019s Secretary for Information and Publicity 1992 to 2002. Deputy Minister 1997 to 2005 (at first at the Ministry of Fisheries and Marine Resources and from 2003 at the Ministry of Justice). Minister of Labour and Social Welfare 2005 &#8211; 2008. Minister of Lands and Resettlement since 2008. Joined SWAPO in 1975 and came up through the party structures in the Erongo Region before independence.He was Chairperson of the SWAPO branch at Arandis for three years and was then responsible for Information and Publicity in the western region. SWAPO internal Secretary for Economic Affairs in the late 1980s. Joined SWAPO Central Committee in 1991. Minister of Works and Transport until 2018; Minister of Agriculture, Water and Forestry (2018 &#8211; 2020).<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Personal<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>Born on 20 March 1954 at Usakos, Erongo Region<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"to